<div class="title">Very Nice</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=tallia&Exact=1">tallia</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; tallia. "Very Nice: An Experience with 2C-I (exp34323)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 16, 2004. erowid.org/exp/34323</div>

<br/>



